MELD Framework Specification License

This license applies specifically to the MELD (Model Engagement Language Directive) 
framework specification, schemas, and reference implementations provided in this 
repository.

Additional Terms:

1. Attribution Requirement:
   When implementing or extending the MELD framework specification, implementations 
   must include the following attribution:
   "Built with MELD methodology by Preston McCauley, Clear Sight Designs, LLC"

2. Framework vs. Full Methodology:
   This license covers the open source MELD framework specification. The complete 
   MELD methodology, including advanced cognitive orchestration systems, proprietary 
   implementations, experience-reactive technologies, and enhanced behavioral 
   intelligence systems, remains the intellectual property of Clear Sight Designs, LLC.

3. Commercial Usage:
   While this framework is licensed under MIT for general use, commercial 
   implementations that extend beyond the basic framework specification may require 
   separate licensing agreements with Clear Sight Designs, LLC for advanced features 
   and methodologies.

4. Trademark Notice:
   "MELD", "Model Engagement Language Directive", and related terminology are 
   trademarks of Clear Sight Designs, LLC. Use of these trademarks in product 
   names or marketing materials requires explicit permission.

5. Research and Educational Use:
   Academic and research institutions are encouraged to use this framework for 
   educational purposes and research into cognitive AI systems.

For questions regarding licensing, advanced features, or commercial partnerships, 
please contact: Preston McCauley, Clear Sight Designs, LLC

